                    <span>"The truth is, there's nothing to find."  Wisdom from the father of Zen, the first to see buddhahood in a grain of sand, in the natural, plain world.  Beautiful.  It will change your life. </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Recant</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
